Package cc.carm.service.minecraft.user.data

Record Class UserKey

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
cc.carm.service.minecraft.user.data.UserKey
Record Components:
id - The user's id, should be unique, usually the auto-increment primary key in database.
uuid - The user's uuid, should be unique, usually the uuid of the user in Minecraft.
name - The user's name, may not be unique, usually the name of the user in Minecraft.
public record UserKey(long id, @NotNull UUID uuid, @NotNull String name) extends Record
A key to identify a user.
